        {"letter": "B", "why_tempting": "Medieval history is a niche topic, so 'limited interest to modern readers' feels like a safe academic concern.", "why_wrong": "The review explicitly anticipates this worry and rebuts it: 'even for the non-medievalist'. Step 5's text-check rules it out — the review goes out of its way to call the book accessible."},
